snippet.title: Starport Delta Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Starport Delta is a space station builder where players must balance resources, station maintenance and resident requirements. Juggle the needs of your population against expanding and dealing with whatever space throws your way.

Wishlist now on Steam, Green Man Gaming and Humble Store!
https://starportdelta.com/steam
https://starportdelta.com/green-man-gaming
https://starportdelta.com/humble

Follow us on social media:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/StarportDelta/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/starportdelta/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CloudfireGames
Website: http://www.starportdelta.com/
